casebody.data:
No. 09-8781. Steven Kalski, Petitioner v. Michael D. Antonovich, et al. 559 U.S. 1034, 130 S. Ct. 2066,

176 L. Ed. 2d 412,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2796. March 29, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of California, Second Appellate District, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
